offset_right = -13.0
offset_bottom = 135.0
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("3_x0g10")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "radians;

- 8444.2b Any action, affirmation, concept or unit of qualia that represents a direct affront to Class I Lifeforms;

- 8444.2c BEACONS OF LIGHT DESCENDING FROM THE SKY, ON THE THIRD DAY OF EXODUS, OVER THE GARDENS OF THE NEBADENESH;

- 8444.2d Mentions of ████ Prime."

[node name="RichTextLabel2" parent="ZoomedContent/5" index="2"]
offset_left = 8.33
offset_top = -135.0
offset_right = 145.33
offset_bottom = 135.0
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("3_x0g10")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "8445. Philosophical Logistics

8445.1 Bargain Sacrifices™ may have causal, epistemological, ontological or paraphysical restrictions in regards to their sacrificial offers, objects of desire, or both.

- 8445.1a Offers that may be characterized with a single action or object must obligatorily causally and chronologically precede"

[node name="6" parent="ZoomedContent" index="5" instance=ExtResource("4_inffp")]

[node name="TextureRect" parent="ZoomedContent/6" index="0"]
texture = ExtResource("2_4qose")

[node name="RichTextLabel" parent="ZoomedContent/6" index="1"]
offset_left = -150.0
offset_top = -135.0
offset_right = -13.0
offset_bottom = 135.0
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("3_x0g10")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "the undertaking of their corresponding objects of desire.

8445.1b Offers that cannot be characterized with a single action or object must begin their causal chain before the undertaking of their corresponding objects of desire, but may be concluded after the initial trigger of their objects of desire. In such cases, the client in question must undergo a remote binding ritual, effective on the"

[node name="RichTextLabel2" parent="ZoomedContent/6" index="2"]
offset_left = 8.33
offset_top = -135.0
offset_right = 145.33
offset_bottom = 135.0
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("3_x0g10")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 13
text = "moment of their Bargain Sacrifice™’s approval, so that their personal identity becomes ontologically linked to the completion of their sacrificial offer."

